7
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:18,320
in order to revive our Chinese nation,

8
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:20,320
you will have our support and hope.

9
00:00:24,640 --> 00:00:26,320
The words of Brother Botang

10
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:30,560
are exactly what I, Cai Yuanpei, want.

11
00:00:31,280 --> 00:00:33,600
Okay, I'm going to reply to Li Yuanhong

12
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:36,080
to take up his post at Peking University as soon as possible.

13
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:39,680
Hold on, Brother Jiemin.

14
00:00:40,480 --> 00:00:43,920
If you want this job, you have to do it right.

15
00:00:44,400 --> 00:00:46,240
Without water, it's hard to build a canal.

16
00:00:46,560 --> 00:00:48,240
If you want to be in this hornet's nest of Peking University,

17
00:00:48,400 --> 00:00:49,920
and make a career out of it.

18
00:00:50,400 --> 00:00:52,880
It's going to take a lot of work!

19
00:00:54,480 --> 00:00:56,400
Please teach me, Brother Botang.

20
00:00:56,640 --> 00:00:58,000
I know you have a well-developed idea

21
00:00:58,160 --> 00:00:59,760
of how to revolutionize education,

22
00:01:00,480 --> 00:01:02,720
but in order to achieve your ambition,

23
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:05,760
you have to meet the conditions set by Li Yuanhong:

24
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,760
sufficient funds,

25
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:09,280
abundance of talented people,

26
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:10,720
transfer of power to lower level.

27
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:12,080
Without these three demands,

28
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:14,640
no matter how good your plans are

29
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:17,600
as the old Beijing saying goes

30
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:19,760
it will be "a blind waste of time".

31
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:26,960
With Brother Botang's help, I, Yuanpei,

32
