The young are promising!

38
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:44,320
This Hu Shizhi fired eight bombshells at once,

39
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:46,880
each hitting the lifeblood of old literature.

40
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:48,720
Baisha, hurry up and arrange

41
