00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,440
You go back first.

101
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:13,600
What does this mean?

102
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,440
Count it. Two dollars and eighty-six cents.

103
00:04:16,080 --> 00:04:17,360
We dried out the magazines.

104
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,760
No need for this.

105
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,760
You still don't want?

106
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,360
How about this?

107
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,200
Count me in to buy thirteen of your magazines.

108
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,680
Sold.

109
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:29,200
Qiaonian.

110
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,960
Wrap thirteen magazines for this sister.

111
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:32,720
That's right!

112
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,760
Actually I had a big fight with my dad

113
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:45,040
that day at home.

114
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,320
When I got up in the morning,

115
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,600
there was no one at home.

116
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:50,000
I was late when no one asked me to go to school.

117
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,640
So I was in a bad mood that day.

118
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,160
My attitude was naturally bad.

119
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:56,000
So I kicked you all out in a rage.

120
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:58,320
Don't take it personally.

121
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,600
We made mistakes before

122
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:00,880
not knowing the school rules.

123
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,560
I also changed your bucket of water.

124
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,720
We both apologize to you.

125
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:06,070
Don't take it to heart.

126
00:05:06,223 --> 00:05:07,121
Don't take it to heart.

127
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:08,240
Then we will not take it to heart.

128
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,429
We're even.

129
00:05:09,551 --> 00:05:10,381
Even.

130
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,800
So what you are saying is

131
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:20,320
you would like me to go to America with Liu Mei.

132
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:21,600
Correct.

133
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,920
And for your brother,

134
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,520
if you agree,

135
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,440
I'll ask Mr. Wu Zhihui

136
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:30,080
to apply for your quotas in the Ministry of Education.

137
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:32,400
But we can't accept other people's funding.

138
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,560
You misunderstood this.

139
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,400
I'm not trying to fund you.

140
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,880
I want you to do me a favor.

141
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:41,280
Liu Mei is my only daughter.

142
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:42,800
She is still young now

143
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:45,200
and has poor ability to live independently.

144
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:48,000
If she goes to study alone,

145
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,840
I won't feel at ease.

146
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:53,200
But if you go with her,

147
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:55,520
you will take care of each other.

148
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,360
I'll be relieved.

149
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:59,840
And as far as the current situation is concerned,

150
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:02,960
studying in the United States is the best choice.

151
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:04,400
This is for you both,

152
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:06,720
I think, a good thing.

153
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:09,600
Uncle, I have my own principles.

154
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,600
We cannot accept this kindness of yours.

155
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,760
Farewell for now.

156
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,463
Yannian.

157
00:06:20,623 --> 00:06:21,831
Yannian.

158
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:24,320
Don't answer me so hastily.

159
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,640
You have to think about it.

160
00:06:26,880 --> 00:06:28,000
But remember,

161
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:30,000
this road I've paved for you,

162
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,600
it is definitely wide,

163
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:34,160
it is definitely flat,

164
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:36,720
it is definitely full of sunlight.

165
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,640
Uncle.

166
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,120
I can reply to you now.

167
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:43,600
We will walk our own road.

168
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:58,560
Brother Jiemin, please!

169
00:06:56,960 --> 00:07:02,794
[Ministry of Education, Republic of China]

170
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,920
I missed you so much.

171
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,760
Jingsheng!

172
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:04,080
I'm forunate to have you as a friend looking out for me.

173
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:06,080
Otherwise,

174
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:08,240
I wouldn't have been able to come back to Beijing.

175
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:12,240
To welcome you, Brother Jiemin,

176
00:07:11,631 --> 00:07:12,649
[Cai Yuanpei, styled Jiemin]

177
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:14,640
I specially prepared a Red Daughter (brand of speciality wine).

178
00:07:13,183 --> 00:07:14,640
[Fan Yuanlian, styled Jingsheng, Minister of Education]

179
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:17,120
Tonight, let's get drunk.

180
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:19,760
Jingsheng, let's get down to business.

181
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,960
Don't get drunk later and delay business.

182
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:26,160
OK, then let's get down to business.

183
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:29,600
Brother Jiemin, Li Yuanhong has made up his mind

184
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:31,440
to invite you to join Peking University.

185
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,040
Six hundred dollars a month.

186
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:35,600
What do you think? When will you take office?

187
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:37,120
As far as I know,

188
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:39,440
the enthusiasm of the capital's academic community for the return of Brother Jiemin

189
00:07:38,424 --> 00:07:40,608
[Tang Erhe, President of Beijing Medical College]

190
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,720
has never been higher!

191
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:42,000
Don't let down

192
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:44,000
the kindness of Brother Jingsheng.

193
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:46,960
Yesterday, someone set off firecrackers in North Square of Peking University,

194
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:46,164
[Shen Yinmo, Professor at Peking University]

195
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:49,440
reportedly to "Welcome President Cai"!

196
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,280
To tell the truth,

197
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:55,520
I've repeatedly weighted the pros and cons before coming

198
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:58,240
and listened to the views of many people.

199
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:01,520
The fact I am in Beijing should make my true feelings self-evident. 

200
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,840
I don't need to say too many of these polite words.

201
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:06,080
It's that, Jingsheng,

202
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:10,320
if President Li approves of my prelminary agreement,

203
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:13,360
then I'll be the president of Peking University.

204
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:16,160
Brother, please tell me about your rules.

205
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:29,040
This is my entire vision.

206
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:30,480
Please let me show it to you.

207
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:41,920
Brother Jiemin.

208
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:46,160
Well, this precedent you're setting is a bit too ambitious.

209
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,360
What's wrong, Jingsheng?

210
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:49,040
It scares the hell out of you?

211
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:53,280
And this is just my initial vision for the school.

212
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:56,080
The second planning scheme of the school...

213
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,200
Wait, wait, wait.

214
00:08:57,520 --> 00:09:01,440
Brother Jiemin, just the first stage, recruiting talent...

215
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,720
You want to, from at home and abroad,

216
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,640
recruit a hundred professors.

217
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:08,880
Arts and sciences director, monthly salary of three hundred silver dollars.

218
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:12,480
Other professors range from one hundred and twenty to two hundred and eighty.

219
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:15,280
How much does it cost to pay the head fee for a year?

220
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:18,080
It is equivalent to dozens of times the current Peking University.

221
00:09:18,560 --> 00:09:20,880
You're demanding a pound of flesh from President Li.

222
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:23,520
Jingsheng, national modernisation

223
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:25,680
must be education-oriented.

224
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:28,240
This is a prerequisite for financial security,

225
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:31,600
You did not recall me to the country

226
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:34,560
to Peking University to be a business-as-usual president.

227
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:37,520
Is this the original intention of President Li?

228
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:40,800
Such a big country

229
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:43,040
would not be short of this funding for Peking University, would it?

230
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:44,720
Minister Fan,

231
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,880
just talk to President Li.

232
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:51,600
Fine. Then I'll go to Li Yuanhong.

233
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:55,280
Good. Jingsheng, my regards.

234
00:09:56,356 --> 00:10:00,398
[Qianmen Chinese-Western Hotel, Beijing]

235
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:58,960
Zhongfu.

236
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,640
You should listen to me.

237
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:02,160
Open a suite for youself.

238
00:10:02,640 --> 00:10:04,400
You can't be too shabby when you're talking to people.

239
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:05,200
No need to put up a show.

240
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:06,400
Just a single room is enough.

241
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:08,000
The people coming to talk about investment are cultured.

242
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,040
They wouldn't pay attention to this.

243
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,080
Just save as much as you can.

244
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,120
You two be careful, here it is.

245
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:13,200
No. The people at the foot of the emperor

246
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:14,240
are all concerned about the show.

247
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:16,000
I can't let you,

248
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:18,240
the famous Chen Duxiu of China, lose face.

249
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:19,920
Buddy,

250
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,680
Give us a suite.

251
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:22,880
No need, no need.

252
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:24,400
Listen to me, just two single rooms.

253
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:25,760
What are you talking about?

254
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:28,000
If he thinks I'm poor, I won't let him join the business.

255
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:30,400
Brother Mengzou, no need to be fussy about accommodations.

256
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,680
But good food is a must.

257
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:32,560
Buddy,

258
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:32,960
you say,

259
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:33,920
Are there any good

260
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,360
lamb hotpot restaurants around here

261
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,400
that you can recommend?

262
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:37,840
Yes, right around the corner.

263
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:40,320
But at this time, it's all for the rickshaw pullers.

264
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:42,000
You two look like respectable people.

265
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,520
Here, you take a few more steps.

266
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:45,600
Not far to the north is Dong Lai Shun.

267
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:47,600
Okay, let's try Dong Lai Shun.

268
00:10:47,760 --> 00:10:48,400
No need, no need.

