309
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,640
This old Beijing lamb.

310
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:27,360
This seasoning is the most delicate.

311
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:30,320
Sesame sauce, soy beans, curd chives.

312
00:12:30,640 --> 00:12:31,680
All essential.

