00:14:18,560 --> 00:14:19,760
Okay, please come inside. Come, come, come. This way.

346
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:20,960
They are still eating.

347
00:14:21,520 --> 00:14:22,080
Alright, alright.

348
00:14:22,160 --> 00:14:22,640
This way!

349
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:23,840
Good.

350
00:14:27,520 --> 00:14:28,240
Xingang!

351
00:14:28,880 --> 00:14:30,557
Mr. Zhongfu!

352
00:14:30,557 --> 00:14:31,564
Hello sir.

353
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:32,320
What a coincidence!

354
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:33,680
Why are you in Beijing?

355
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:34,960
After Shanghai,

356
00:14:35,040 --> 00:14:36,640
we both came to Beijing to study.

357
00:14:36,800 --> 00:14:37,760
Sit down. Sit down.

358
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:41,200
She had just passed the Peking University entrance exam,

359
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:43,280
But now Peking University doesn't accept female students.

360
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:45,360
So Bailan worked as a tutor in Dongjiaominxiang

361
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:46,560
tutoring French at the same time,

362
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:48,640
to work and study in France in the future.

363
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:50,800
Today, she just got paid.

364
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:52,320
The two of us planned to come here to have a nice meal.

365
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:53,840
I didn't expect to meet you, sir.

366
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,360
What a coincidence!

367
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:57,120
You are at Peking University now.

368
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:59,280
I wanted a chance to visit Peking University anyway.

369
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,960
You can show me around when you have time.

370
00:15:01,040 --> 00:15:01,760
Of course, sir.

371
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:02,560
You don't know it,

372
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:04,160
but you're a celebrity at Peking Univesity.

373
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:05,600
Many students and teachers are all reading

374
00:15:05,680 --> 00:15:07,280
that "New Youth" magazine you founded.

375
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:08,400
So admirable!

376
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,240
Server!

377
00:15:10,560 --> 00:15:10,800
Coming!

378
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:12,160
Remove the hotpot separator.

379
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:13,200
We'll eat from the same pot.

380
00:15:13,520 --> 00:15:13,760
Sure.

381
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:15,440
And add another two plates of mutton.

382
00:15:15,840 --> 00:15:16,480
Will do.

383
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:19,120
Anyone can tell at a glance that you're birds of a feather,

384
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,800
dipping your food next to each other.

385
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:22,320
Have a nice meal.

386
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:23,360
Yes.

387
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:25,920
Here, eat.

388
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:28,320
Go ahead, eat.

389
00:15:29,040 --> 00:15:30,080
Thank you, sir.

390
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:02,640
Eat.

391
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:15,280
Zhongfu,

392
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:17,360
You've frightened the kids.

393
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:19,360
Mr. Zhongfu,

394
00:16:19,520 --> 00:16:20,880
have you not eaten for several days?

395
00:16:22,400 --> 00:16:25,920
This is a method I've just learned from the labouring masses.

396
00:16:26,880 --> 00:16:28,000
It's exceptionally delightful.

397
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,440
An absolute delight!

398
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,320
Hurry up and eat. Gotta pick up a fare.

399
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:41,680
What fare?

400
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:42,800
Are you pulling a rickshaw?

401
00:16:43,360 --> 00:16:45,600
Pulling in investors! Hurry.

402
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:46,240
Alright!

403
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:48,400
Brother Jiemin,

404
00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:51,840
from today on, you will be the principal of Peking University.

405
00:16:53,680 --> 00:16:54,480
Master Cai,

406
00:16:54,800 --> 00:16:57,520
this is a heavy responsibility to shoulder.

407
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:59,120
Please.

408
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:03,360
Jingsheng, this is hard to come by.

409
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:07,360
I will cherish it.

410
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:14,800
I thank everyone for their help.

411
00:17:15,840 --> 00:17:18,720
I, Yuanpei, will certainly fulfill the mission.

412
00:17:20,080 --> 00:17:22,720
Master Cai, when do you plan to assume office?

413
00:17:22,960 --> 00:17:24,560
And where will you start?

414
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:27,440
It is for you to decide when.

415
00:17:27,600 --> 00:17:28,720
And as for where to start,

416
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:30,560
I think the first step

417
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:32,000
is to recruit talent.

418
00:17:32,320 --> 00:17:35,680
First of all, those from the liberal arts.

419
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:37,520
I would like to find someone

420
00:17:37,840 --> 00:17:42,240
who can raise the banner of innovation to be the dean of liberal arts.

421
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:44,560
Everyone present, please help me think

422
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:46,800
who is able to take on this important task.

423
00:17:47,200 --> 00:17:48,880
This liberal arts dean

424
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:52,400
must be sympathetic to you,

425
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:54,480
but also be of noble character and high prestige.

426
00:17:54,800 --> 00:17:56,320
Must be a learned academic,

427
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:58,640
but also with the ability to charge through enemy lines.

428
00:17:59,280 --> 00:18:00,560
Such a person is not easy to find.

429
00:18:01,280 --> 00:18:02,480
I've thought of someone.

430
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:05,360
Chen Zhongfu, or Chen Duxiu.

431
00:18:06,240 --> 00:18:09,920
This is a person who is leading the trends of today's China.

432
00:18:10,320 --> 00:18:12,880
He is certain to be able to take on this important task.

433
00:18:13,520 --> 00:18:14,960
I also thought of Chen Duxiu.

434
00:18:18,480 --> 00:18:20,800
Are you know Chen Duxiu well?

435
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:22,320
Only as an acquaintance.

436
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:24,720
But I've read every issue

437
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:26,320
of his magazine "New Youth."

438
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:28,080
Yes, his magazine "New Youth."

439
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:28,960
I also read it.

440
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:34,240
Brother Zhongfu and I are old friends.

441
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:36,240
Qian Xuantong said that

442
00:18:36,480 --> 00:18:37,920
Chen Duxiu has come to Beijing.

443
00:18:38,080 --> 00:18:40,160
He's asked for a meeting to commission an article.

444
00:18:41,600 --> 00:18:43,200
Where is he living? Do you know?

445
00:18:43,360 --> 00:18:44,160
I will ask around.

446
00:18:44,320 --> 00:18:46,640
Yes. Please.

447
00:18:48,080 --> 00:18:50,080
Zhongfu, listen to me. Zhongfu.

448
00:18:50,560 --> 00:18:53,040
That's one hundred thousand shares acquired in one go.

449
00:18:57,600 --> 00:18:58,480
Zhongfu.

450
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:01,600
It's great. Several hundred thousand shares.

451
00:19:03,280 --> 00:19:04,240
We've done it this time.

452
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:06,560
This time, we can go all out.

453
00:19:07,360 --> 00:19:08,480
It seems like in Beijing our "New Youth"

454
00:19:08,560 --> 00:19:09,360
has a lot of influence.

455
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:09,920
That's for sure.

456
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:10,720
Huge potential market.

457
00:19:10,960 --> 00:19:11,760
Definitely.

458
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:14,480
Now I believe the words you spoke last year.

459
00:19:14,960 --> 00:19:15,680
Which words?

460
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:17,440
You said, give you ten years.

461
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:20,000
And you will change the thinking of our compatriots.

462
00:19:21,520 --> 00:19:23,760
Now it looks like it won't take ten years.

463
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:27,440
We must set up a banquet.

464
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:28,320
To celebrate.

465
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:28,800
Yes.

466
00:19:28,960 --> 00:19:30,480
I will ask Xingang and Bailan to come.

467
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:31,120
Quickly.

468
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:31,520
Yes.

469
00:19:33,600 --> 00:19:36,880
Dropped a seed and sprouted a shoot.

470
00:19:37,760 --> 00:19:41,200
What branch, what leaf, what flower will bloom?

471
00:19:41,520 --> 00:19:44,480
Bear what kind of fruit? Grind -

472
00:20:13,360 --> 00:20:14,560
Brother Jiemin.

473
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:44,800
Brother Zhongfu.

474
00:20:46,160 --> 00:20:47,280
How did you find me here?

475
00:20:47,520 --> 00:20:48,800
I will always be able to find you.

476
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:52,800
Come this way, sir.

477
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:56,400
Please come inside.

478
00:20:56,640 --> 00:20:57,520
In here.

479
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:03,120
Please sit, sir.

480
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:05,360
Alright. Please sit.

481
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:08,640
Have a seat.

482
00:21:08,800 --> 00:21:09,840
Yes.

483
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:20,880
Sir, sit.

484
00:21:21,040 --> 00:21:22,080
Brother Zhongfu.

485
00:21:23,840 --> 00:21:25,360
I have the impression...

486
00:21:27,360 --> 00:21:31,440
that I am a few years your senior.

487
00:21:32,080 --> 00:21:33,460
I was born in the year of the rabbit，

488
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:35,680
in the fifth year of the reign of Emperor Guangxu (1879)

489
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:37,440
We have the same zodiac sign.

490
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:40,120
I was born in the sixth year of the reign of Emperor Tongzhi. (1867)

491
00:21:40,320 --> 00:21:43,120
You see, I remembered I am a cycle older than you.

492
00:21:47,840 --> 00:21:51,040
Do you still remember when we were in Shanghai twenty years ago?

493
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:53,840
Together on an assassination squad,

494
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:55,680
prototyping a bomb?

495
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:57,200
How could I forget?

496
00:21:57,840 --> 00:22:00,240
Couldn't manufacture it, narrowly escaped with our lives.

497
00:22:00,560 --> 00:22:02,080
Even now, I often see it in my dreams.

498
00:22:04,080 --> 00:22:05,120
True, true.

499
00:22:05,440 --> 00:22:08,000
At the time, if you hadn't given that shove...

500
00:22:08,320 --> 00:22:10,640
I would not be sitting in front of you today.

501
00:22:10,960 --> 00:22:12,640
Dead as a doornail, long ago.

502
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:14,400
Brother Zhongfu,

503
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:16,640
you saved my life.

504
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:18,480
I have to properly thank you.

505
00:22:18,560 --> 00:22:20,160
You're too kind. You're overstating it.

506
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:22,960
Twelve years ago,

507
00:22:23,280 --> 00:22:25,360
I was the age you are now.

508
00:22:26,400 --> 00:22:27,440
At that time,

509
00:22:27,600 --> 00:22:29,840
there was nothing I was afraid of doing, nothing I was afraid of saying. 

510
00:22:30,080 --> 00:22:31,520
I was brave and unyielding.

511
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,360
But now I am old.

512
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,360
No longer have that edge.

513
00:22:35,840 --> 00:22:38,640
And not as driven as times gone by.

514
00:22:39,680 --> 00:22:41,440
You're not doing so bad.

515
00:22:41,760 --> 00:22:43,200
Nowadays, you, Chen Duxiu,

516
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:45,680
has raised in China the two big banners 

517
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:47,120
of science and democracy.

518
00:22:48,960 --> 00:22:51,200
And what have you brought the country?

519
00:22:51,680 --> 00:22:53,360
A breath of fresh air.

520
00:22:54,080 --> 00:22:56,560
I read every issue of your magazine "New Youth."

521
00:22:56,600 --> 00:22:58,480
With each reading, there's always something to be gained.

522
00:22:58,640 --> 00:23:00,560
Sir, if you would like to submit a manuscript,

523
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:02,400
I would be extremely grateful.

524
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:06,240
That is a matter of course. Naturally I will contribute.

525
00:23:09,040 --> 00:23:10,400
I came here today

526
00:23:13,120 --> 00:23:15,120
to ask you for some help.

527
00:23:15,760 --> 00:23:16,640
Please go on, sir.

528
00:23:18,160 --> 00:23:19,600
Starting yesterday, I have been

529
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:22,480
formally appointed the president of Peking Univesity.

530
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:30,480
Take a look. Letter of appointment.

531
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:40,000
Congratulations, sir.

532
00:23:44,640 --> 00:23:48,960
I would like you to come to Peking University to be the Dean of Liberal Arts.

533
00:23:49,840 --> 00:23:51,280
Lend me a hand.

534
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:53,360
Lend Peking University a hand.

535
00:23:53,840 --> 00:23:56,880
I hope Brother Zhongfu would not decline.

536
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:06,320
I would like to thank Brother Jiemin for the support.

537
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:08,080
But this is very sudden.

538
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:10,080
I'm not mentally prepared.

539
00:24:12,320 --> 00:24:13,280
Zhongfu,

540
00:24:13,760 --> 00:24:16,920
the Dean of Liberal Arts is equivalent to the Deputy President of Peking University,

541
00:24:17,040 --> 00:24:20,080
leading the various disciplines of the humanities and social science.

542
00:24:20,560 --> 00:24:23,840
Aren't you currently advocating and calling for

543
00:24:24,080 --> 00:24:25,440
democratic science?

544
00:24:26,240 --> 00:24:30,400
I think this would be your best stage to do so.

545
00:24:32,480 --> 00:24:34,880
Precisely because it's a serious responsibility,

546
00:24:35,120 --> 00:24:37,440
